Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:16.18,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\i1}We used to talk all night until the sun rose,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:19.02,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\i1}And held hands till the sun went under the horizon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:24.28,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,258)\i1}Let's walk together like this forever, like light and shadow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:28.82,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(258,0)}I stand in the city, staring off into space with lonely eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:34.16,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can't find warmth on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:39.67,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,258)}By meeting you, I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:45.50,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(258,0)}How much strength love could give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:50.76,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Even if we part and meet again, I want to meet at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:56.06,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Then we'll hold hands to ensure we'll never be separated again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:01.27,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can't sleep by myself, 'cause I can't dream without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:07.03,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}So take me to a place where uncertainty can't reach us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:12.28,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}And let us bring light to the night sky with no stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:14.78,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\i1}So long as you're with me, I can go to world's end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:17.79,ED03 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\i1}Even if it's a path I can't walk on my own,{\i0}
