Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.10,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,This is him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:52.86,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.40,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:00.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:04.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al in the armor... which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:09.16,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:10.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:11.58,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:12.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:13.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:16.38,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad to see you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:14.50,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.88,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Your armor's hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:24.18,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I'm so glad to see you're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:29.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,For worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But where the heck are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:43.20,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.53,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Humans came out of his stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hohen...heim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:53.67,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,An arm and a leg made of steel, and a suit of armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.76,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the Elric Brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's not him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.39,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mistaking me for somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.14,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.14,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Hohen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:13.64,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're talking about Van Hohenheim?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.90,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What is your relationship with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:19.15,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He's... our dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.40,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:27.87,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise! He ended up having kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:36.71,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't your last names Elric?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Elric is our mother's maiden name!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.84,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.42,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,So, where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:47.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You look just like Hohenheim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:51.35,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.81,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,And he's even had kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.77,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.35,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, this man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:57.56,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.73,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,And you're missing your left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.49,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:07.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.41,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,A broken bone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:24.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.72,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Now for your ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:35.14,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You two are important to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.23,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be too reckless with your bodies, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:41.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He used alchemy without a single hand motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.19,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,And he didn't make the rest of my armor thinner, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:47.07,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's not equivalent exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.07,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:52.08,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,It's unreal! How could your insides be in such a state?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:55.70,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask you the same exact question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.08,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:01.79,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You can eat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:02.84,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:09.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a human sacrifice, so don't kill him for my sake. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.55,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:14.68,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,He's useless to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:20.44,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, the Homunculi call him "Father".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.69,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who created them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:23.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.07,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he patched us up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.20,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.78,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Your attitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:34.33,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as those who laugh at humans for being foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:39.37,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Do you consider insects crawling about the Earth to be foolish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:46.51,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Even if insects struggle, the difference between you and them is so great that you don't exactly give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:51.64,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,That's precisely how I feel about you humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:59.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate you healing our wounds,\Nbut I don't think I can get along with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:02.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you're the cause of everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:04.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of you quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:06.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be worrying about the small fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:09.28,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're calling me small fry now, runt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Runt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've got their leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:41.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How can he use alchemy without a single hand motion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.44,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:22.18,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use alchemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:24.56,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Ed! Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What did that geezer do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.49,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we use alchemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:40.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, these tiny beings are unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:44.08,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,They start to think they're at the top of the world as soon as they gain some power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.29,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even know what exactly they're using.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:52.88,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think all this prosperity was created with the powers of humans only?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:56.09,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,How laughable, fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:02.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You promised you'd tell me as soon as we got out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:03.85,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:08.02,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember making promises with you insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.69,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking too much, Envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:12.86,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.78,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,He could be good for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.66,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I may be able to create another pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:29.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's... a philosopher's stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.29,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.55,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,So you're planning to do it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.92,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He's creating a Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:40.26,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to inject the philosopher's stone into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:44.14,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,If all goes well, a homunculus with a human base will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:52.73,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, most humans end up dying because they aren't capable of fighting the stone's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'll let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.20,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, Envy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:00.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we use alchemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Geezer! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:09.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He has people waiting for his return!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.88,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Humans can't shoot me if I do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.72,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:23.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.56,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.56,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.73,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:29.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:32.98,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I came to this country looking for a philosopher's stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.44,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,And he's just going to give it to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.99,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly what I wished for!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.86,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:43.62,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Then as you wish, it's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:00.26,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I... I told you not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.09,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,...to interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:10.77,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine... Just wait for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:15.36,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who will become the Emperor of Xing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.57,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,...Ling Yao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:39.46,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is a brat doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.42,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:43.43,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.14,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it to good use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.43,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.64,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,It's all yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:50.64,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:53.27,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that I'll accept you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.27,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't people normally be against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.82,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the Emperor of Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:02.86,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,How do you expect me to do that if I can't even accept a few dozen people in my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.53,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I like decisive guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.49,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,But you'd better not regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:11.25,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:17.25,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,If I return empty-handed, how could I possibly face my servant who cut her own arm off to save me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:21.13,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I want power...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:26.26,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Absolute power that will help me protect and gain more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.14,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I knew the risks from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.18,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I like your greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:36.94,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, show me how prepared you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:53.41,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, the guy who owned this body?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:58.04,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but now it belongs to me, Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:01.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Not Ling, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Greed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:14.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're that Greed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:18.19,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "that" Greed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.23,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The one at Dublith...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.44,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so what Greed are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:26.20,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,The Greed that came before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.57,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.12,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:33.50,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a different Greed from the one you guys know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Ling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.63,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He was an interesting brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:41.25,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He accepted me in a matter of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:46.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No way! There's no way he's that easy to take control of!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me! Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:49.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ling!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.32,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.48,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.74,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:09.86,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,He's a person, but at the same time, he's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:15.33,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, a lot of these guys aren't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.87,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Shao May!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.88,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad to see you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:22.75,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how worried I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.88,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I don't really get it, but is this some tearful reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:34.22,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they aren't working together with the Homunculi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:36.81,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.18,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.40,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sir Edward?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.40,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.32,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see him anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.94,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pointing right at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:50.45,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,That small one is the Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:12.43,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,You toyed with my pure heart, you midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Speak for yourself, midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.97,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Ishbalan I didn't get to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.89,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,The disobedient people, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:26.48,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who uses destructive alchemy and continues to interfere with our plans, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.43,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to her, Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:19.06,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:28.94,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of them, Gluttony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.70,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He can't use alchemy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.70,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:39.70,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:41.29,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:45.50,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,You stepped all over a maiden's heart,\Nand on top of that, you kidnapped Shao May!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.92,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Divine punishment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:50.42,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,...for all of you!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:55.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We still can't use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:03.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.19,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,How can you two use alchemy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.69,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.74,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How can Scar and that little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:14.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:16.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No idea, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:19.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This could be our chance to fill them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:20.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:25.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you the truth behind the Ishbal rebellion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.92,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The death of the child which became the trigger of the rebellion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:35.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...was caused by him, disguised as a military officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:40.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They're behind it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:54.24,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I'll have to ask you to explain this in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:03.62,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.92,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Why did my people have to fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:11.92,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on your answer, I'll send you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:12.96,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:17.09,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I won't send you to God, where my fellow Ishbalans reside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:20.51,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Think of yourselves as undeserving of eternal rest or redemption!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.52,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:31.69,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad for a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:34.78,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Greed, get rid of the intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.03,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:44.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to believe it, Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.50,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:55.72,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:59.09,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be Ling from the Yao clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:02.10,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,A little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:05.10,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Soft body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:14.23,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, how can you use alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:20.95,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you really are using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.37,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Human destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:26.54,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,No, decomposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:36.13,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,A second later, and I would have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.42,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:46.60,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Shao May... Run...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:49.27,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:51.98,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.74,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I never asked you to save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:04.74,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,They're ruthless toward humans who are of no benefit to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.67,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,There's way too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:19.09,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You two didn't run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:29.52,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Scar, could you take this girl and get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.35,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to let me escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:35.61,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I killed those doctors...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:38.82,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I want to beat the hell out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:41.86,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I don't even want to ask you for any favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:44.62,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, it's more important to take this girl somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.78,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:53.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, my brother and I are important to them in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:57.21,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we stay here, they won't kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:02.76,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I won't be able to protect\Nthat girl and escape from here at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:06.39,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't have the slightest intention of running away, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:10.27,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He decomposed water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:23.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, let me know before you do stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.45,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:31.29,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Igniting hydrogen? That's clever of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:34.87,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:36.92,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.00,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.46,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony, track him by scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:46.30,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of lives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.76,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You've died too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:52.31,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That was a nice kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.89,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I think this'll be more fun than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:58.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:01.90,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:02.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Give Ling back his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.70,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,No can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:14.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do about your country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What about Lan Fan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.85,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Father! I got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:29.85,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.30,0:21:33.52,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Take him upstairs, where Wrath is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:38.90,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... Always screwing around with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:43.73,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you guys behave, we won't do a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:48.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:50.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:52.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...is inside of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:33.84,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You used up your regeneration abilities, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:37.26,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:53.03,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I will recreate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:55.16,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,With your memories, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.33,0:24:04.21,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Humans in chaos, struggle and writhe in agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.21,0:24:07.09,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Because that serves as proof that one is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.71,0:24:11.97,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And struggle and kneel before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.59,0:24:17.14,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.14,0:24:21.14,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 29, Struggle of the Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.68,0:24:26.40,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Will the man who had his limbs twisted be able to stand again?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
